<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.7">
<l>āyēyiv vulakattu niṟpaṉavun tirivaṉavu</l>
<l>nīyēmaṟ ṟoruporuḷu miṉṟinī niṉṟamaiyā</l>
<l>ṉōyēmūp piṟappuppiṟappup piṇiyēyeṉ ṟivaiyoḻiyak</l>
<l>kūyēko ḷaṭiyēṉaik koṭuvulakaṅ kāṭṭēlē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ah! Because of your having stood without any meaning other than</l>
<l>you in those beings that stand and roam in this world,</l>
<l>so that these, namely pain, old age, dying, birth [and] disease cease</l>
<l>just call me with [bad] karma. don’t show [me] the cruel world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
